            <p><span data-custom-class="body_text">We may update this <span data-custom-class="body_text"><span data-custom-class="body_text">privacy policy</span></span>&nbsp;from time to time. The updated version will be indicated by an updated &ldquo;Revised&rdquo; date and the updated version will be effective as soon as it is accessible. If we make material changes to this <span data-custom-class="body_text"><span data-custom-class="body_text">privacy policy</span></span>, we may notify you either by prominently posting a notice of such changes or by directly sending you a notification. We encourage you to review this <span data-custom-class="body_text"><span data-custom-class="body_text">privacy policy</span></span>&nbsp;frequently to be informed of how we are protecting your information.</span></p>
